title: 272. Andy, Mike Yoder & DJ CTI: Elon Musk's Twitter Shares, Texas Transporting Migrants To DC & California DA's Warning
itunes:title: 272. Andy, Mike Yoder & DJ CTI: Elon Musk's Twitter Shares, Texas Transporting Migrants To DC & California DA's Warning
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ are joined in the studio by Attorney-at-law Mike Yoder. They discuss Elon Musk's recent decision to purchase a 9.2% stake in Twitter, Texas sending migrants in busses to the nation's capital, and the California DA who opposed the release of Sacramento's mass shooting suspect.
